item.title: CVE-2020-7831|2024-09-17T02:12:07.149Z -- inogard -- ebiz4u%20cviewer%20object%20axecm.dll
item.description: A vulnerability in the web-based contract management service interface Ebiz4u of INOGARD could allow an victim user to download any file. The attacker is able to use startup menu directory via directory traversal for automatic execution. The victim user need to reboot, however.
